FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://api.dailysmarty.com/

# DailySmarty

DailySmarty is a knowledge logging service that allows for users to share what they learn each day. The API allows for 3rd party clients to query posts and securely post to the system via the API.

## List All Posts [/posts]

