### Create a New Post [POST]

You may create your own post using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a title _(required)_, content, and array of post links.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "Implementing the Facade Pattern in Rails 14",
            "content": "The Facade design pattern helps to streamline the setup code in Rails controllers and organize where initial values are stored. This guide provides helpful examples for how this can be implemented in a Rails app.",
            "post_links_attributes": [
                {
                    "link_url": "https://medium.com/kkempin/facade-design-pattern-in-ruby-on-rails-710aa88326f"
                },
                {
                    "link_url": "https://medium.com/@ryakh/facade-pattern-on-rails-d65b86cdb5b1"
                }
            ]
        }

